                        <h3>Making Payments</h3>
                        <p>We have about three methods by which you can make payment for the services we render to you or fund your wallet in advance for future services.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Method One: <br> Online Payment</li>
                            <li>Method Two: <br> Mobile/ATM Money Transfer</li>
                            <li>Method Three: <br> Bank Deposit</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a name="addnew"></a>
                        <h3>Online Payment: </h3>
                        <p>This is the fastest method as your payment transaction will be instantly initiated from our website or any other web payment platform. Your payment will be instantly acknowledged and confirmed using this option.</p>
                        <p>To Make Online Payment to COINMAC Properties, simple fill this form by entering the amount you want to pay and click on Pay Now button</p>
                        <p>
                            <form id="payform">
                                <script src="https://js.paystack.co/v1/inline.js"></script>
                                <input type="hidden" value="<%=userdata.userid%>" name="userid">
                                <input type="hidden" value="<%=userdata.name%>" name="depositorname">
                                <input type="hidden" value="Online Payment" name="methodofpayment">
                                <input type="hidden" value="FCMB" name="bankpaidto">
                                <input type="hidden" name="payref" value="paystack">
                                

                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="pay_amount">Enter Amount (&#8358;)</label>
                                    <input type="number" class="form-control" id="pay_amount" value="0" name="amountpaid">
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-center">
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default"  onclick="payWithPaystack()">Pay Now</button>
                                </div>
                            </form>

                        </p>
                        <hr>
                        
